long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Extension is a subsidiary of Munbyn printer, please connect to a Munbyn thermal label printer via usb cable to print. This Extension allows you to print the currently displayed Web Page. You can press "Ctrl + P" to open the print preview interface, select Munbyn printer and click "Print"  to print what you want to print.
